we can use a lock-free approach, which looks like this
do {
currentPosition =   position.get()
nextPosition += fragmentCount;
 } while (!position.cas(currentPosition, nextPosition))

Example https://github.com/zeebe-io/zeebe/blob/develop/util/src/main/java/io/zeebe/util/sched/channel/ActorConditions.java#L33

